  "mixStrategy": "Three-layer frequency separation: Warm Pad bass anchors the low register (MIDI 38-48) with slow, sustained root notes providing a warm foundation. Choir Pad chords fill the mid register (MIDI 50-67) with open-voiced sus2 and maj7 voicings, never more than 3 notes at once, changing every 8-16 seconds. New Age Pad melody floats in the upper register (MIDI 64-79) with gentle arch-shaped phrases that breathe and drift. All layers follow the same harmonic rhythm: Dsus2 \u2192 Gmaj7 \u2192 Dsus2 \u2192 Asus2 \u2192 Gmaj7 \u2192 Dsus2. Energy arc rises gently from 0.3 to 0.6 at the midpoint, then descends back to 0.3 for a peaceful close. No rhythmic drive \u2014 all parts flow like calm water.",
